feature_df <- read_csv("features.csv") %>% 
  
  filter(! is.na(cgm_days),
         cgm_days >= 6,
         between(a1c_value, 5.5, 11.5)) %>% 
  
  # In protocol H, there are multiple HbA1c recordings on the same day
  # This was likely to calibrate. Taking the "first" one from each day.
  group_by(id, a1c_date) %>% 
  sample_n(1) %>% 
  ungroup() %>% 
  
  group_by(id) %>% 
  
  mutate(a1c_count = n(),
         race = ifelse(race == "Black/African American",
                                                 "Black",
                                                 race),
         ethnicity = ifelse(ethnicity == "Non-Hispanic",
                                                 "Not Hispanic or Latino",
                                                 ethnicity)
         ) %>% 
  ungroup()
